      "content": "That sounds okay on paper, but the truth is the candidate only changed their mind because the latest polling in the swing districts looked terrible for the old position. If we tell them it's about \"long-term vision\" and the reporter digs and asks why the policy actually changed, we're going to look even worse. How do we explain the actual change without admitting it was just a response to the polls?",
